    "Therefore, developers must recognize the sensitivity of medical data and the need for ethical considerations to be integrated from the outset of AI development for medical applications.",
    "Such early integration of ethics serves not only to enhance the accuracy and reliability of AI tools but also to safeguard the dignity and rights of individuals whose data are used in these systems.",
